'From Squeak2.8alpha of 16 February 2000 [latest update: #2174] on 22 May 2000 at 12:20:34 pm'!"Change Set:		OCTweaksDate:			22 May 2000Author:			Andreas RaabTwo tweaks for OrderedCollection. Makes removals from (large) OCs faster. Make #removeAt: return the removed object."!!OrderedCollection methodsFor: 'removing' stamp: 'ar 5/22/2000 12:19'!removeAt: index	| removed |	removed _ self at: index.	self removeIndex: index + firstIndex - 1.	^removed! !!OrderedCollection methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'ar 5/22/2000 12:17'!removeIndex: removedIndex	array 		replaceFrom: removedIndex 		to: lastIndex - 1 		with: array 		startingAt: removedIndex+1.	array at: lastIndex put: nil.	lastIndex _ lastIndex - 1.! !